### Login user to get JWT
POST {{MovieDatabase.Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation{ loginUser(request: { email: \"admin@example.com\", password: \"test\" }) { id username email role token expireTime } }"
}

